      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、お待たせ……って、寝てるのか？\n緊張の糸が切れたんだな。昨日は眠れなかったようだし",
      "startTime": 14.0999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "出来れば、このまま寝かせてやりたいが……\nおーいすみれ、起きてくれ。新幹線に乗り遅れるぞ",
      "startTime": 23.6502491958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "むにゃ……お兄ちゃん……\nおんぶ……",
      "startTime": 34.8350117366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "寝ぼけてるのか？　だが新幹線の時間もあるし……\n仕方ない。すみれ、俺の背中に乗ってくれ",
      "startTime": 42.9156210721,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
