      "text": "うん……お兄ちゃん、ありがと……\nむにゃ……すぅ……すぅ……",
      "startTime": 53.7068260829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ、本当に乗って来たな……\nよし、ちゃんと駅まで連れて行くからな",
      "startTime": 66.366666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁい……むにゃ……\nえへへ、お兄ちゃんの背中、おっきくて大好き……",
      "startTime": 74.4039919217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
