      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "……もうダメだぁ……恥ずかしいよぅ……\n明日からどんな顔して学校に行けばいいのぉ……",
      "startTime": 89.066666476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ、そんなにへこまなくても大丈夫だ\n途中からタクシーに乗ったし",
      "startTime": 96.2832335662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "でもでもでも！　教室から校門の前までは\nおんぶしてもらっちゃったじゃないですか……！",
      "startTime": 101.7707699139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "小さい子みたいに甘えちゃうなんて……\n重かったですよね、本当にごめんなさいっ！",
      "startTime": 108.1374365806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "気にしてないし、重くもなかったよ\nそれに、今日授業の様子を見て、改めて思ったんだ",
      "startTime": 114.5833717901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "な、何をですか……？　あっ、まさか……\n私、授業中張り切り過ぎて、子供っぽかったですか！？",
      "startTime": 122.0987064361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ。すみれが、いつも一生懸命頑張ってるんだって\n思ったんだ。仕事でも、学校でも、プライベートでもな",
      "startTime": 130.5999977748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、もっと甘えてくれたっていいんだ\n俺はすみれのマネージャーで、東京のお兄ちゃんだから",
      "startTime": 139.6161059439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーで、東京のお兄ちゃんか……えへへ\nそれならたまに\nおんぶじゃなくて手を繋いでほしいです",
      "startTime": 154.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ところで……おんぶされてるところ\nそんなに大勢には見られてませんよね？",
      "startTime": 162.2415114402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "大勢かは分からないが、何人かとすれ違ったよ",
      "startTime": 165.6748468081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
