      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ、さすがベテランだな……\n気持ちの切り替えが一瞬とは……",
      "startTime": 182.6666776657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
