      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_14_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（本番まであと少し……演奏終了まで）\n（すみれにドッキリがバレないことを祈ろう）",
